videos.description: Martin Krampelj denies an alley-oop attempt off the backboard.
videos.headline: Creighton's Krampelj pins it off the backboard

videos.description: Silas Melson knocks down a 3-pointer deep behind the three-point line for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Melson buries deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Silas Melson picks up a steal and a bucket in transition on the other end for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Melson gets the bucket plus the foul

videos.description: Toby Hegner knocks down a 3-pointer from the corner to put Creighton ahead in the first half over Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Creighton's Hegner drains corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Silas Melson knocks down a 3-pointer deep behind the three-point line for the second time.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Melson buries another deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Johnathan Williams slams it home out of the break for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Williams rises up for the alley-oop

videos.description: Zach Norvell Jr. finishes in transition for Gonzaga after a foul.
videos.headline: Norvell takes some contact and gets the bucket

videos.description: Johnathan Williams finishes the bucket after taking a foul to continue a big run for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Williams finishes acrobatic shot with a foul

videos.description: Silas Melson knocks down a 3-pointer from the corner after a big block.
videos.headline: Melson turns a block into a 3-pointer

videos.description: Rui Hachimura gets a huge rejection for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Hachimura picks up big block

videos.description: Killian Tillie rises up and throws it down over Martin Krampelj.
videos.headline: Tillie puts defender on poster

videos.description: Zach Norvell Jr. picks up the hoop plus the harm to extend the Gonzaga lead to 13.
videos.headline: Norvell gets and-1 to go
